<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Privacy Policy - Birthday Reminder</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <h1>Birthday Reminder Application</h1>
      <nav>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
          <li><a href="/add">Add Customer</a></li>
        </ul>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
      <h2>Privacy Policy</h2>

      <div class="policy-content">
        <p>Last updated: <%= new Date().toLocaleDateString() %></p>

        <h3>1. Information We Collect</h3>
        <p>
          Our Birthday Reminder Application collects and stores the following
          information about your customers:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Username</li>
          <li>Email address</li>
          <li>Gender</li>
          <li>Date of birth</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>2. How We Use The Information</h3>
        <p>
          The information we collect is used solely for the purpose of sending
          birthday greetings to your customers on their birthday. We do not use
          this data for any other purposes or share it with third parties.
        </p>

        <h3>3. Data Security</h3>
        <p>
          We implement reasonable security measures to protect the personal
          information we collect and maintain. However, no security system is
          impenetrable, and we cannot guarantee the security of our systems
          100%.
        </p>

        <h3>4. Email Communications</h3>
        <p>
          By providing customer email addresses, you confirm that you have the
          necessary permission to send them birthday greetings. The application
          will automatically send emails to customers on their birthdays.
        </p>

        <h3>5. Changes To This Policy</h3>
        <p>
          We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will notify
          you of any changes by posting the new privacy policy on this page.
        </p>

        <h3>6. Contact Us</h3>
        <p>
          If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us
          at:
        </p>
        <p>Email: browndevop@gmail.com</p>
      </div>

      <a href="/" class="btn">Back to Home</a>
    </div>

    <!-- footer -->

    <footer>
      <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Birthday Reminder App</p>
      <p>Keeping connections with your customers</p>
      <div class="footer-links">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/add">Add Customer</a>
        <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>
      </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
